1+|z|^2=\frac{|v|^2+|u|^2}{|v|^2}=|v|^{-2}
uv=|uv|=\frac{|u/v|}{|v|^{-2}}=\frac{|z|}{1+|z|^2}
u^2=uv\frac{u}{v}=z\frac{|z|}{1+|z|^2}\ \ \ \Rightarrow\ \ \ u=\pm\  z^{1/2}\sqrt{\frac{|z|}{1+|z|^2}}
v^2=uv/\frac{u}{v}=z^{-1}\frac{|z|}{1+|z|^2}\ \ \ \Rightarrow\ \ \ v=\pm\  z^{-1/2}\sqrt{\frac{|z|}{1+|z|^2}}\ 
